node.text:
Struggling with writer's block, a novelist finds inspiration when she meets a down-on-his-luck oddball who constantly changes personas and alter egos to cope with the past and avoid reality.

With: @ilizasheslinger @davidkoechner @cleopatracoleman @trezzo_ @nickthune #ad #therightonemovie

node.title: Watch “The Right One” now on iTunes and ON Demand 🙏🥰💖
